details.name: Illuminate
details.description: Channels light energy, building power the longer it's channeled.  Once released, a wave is sent forth that deals damage and gives vision in its path.  The longer it is channeled, the more damage is dealt. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Allows Illuminate to heal allies during the day for the same amount as its damage values, and causes Illuminate to not require channeling.
